-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33228,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/08\/18\/shukr-for-small-things\/","url_meta":{"origin":19144,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Gratitude: Be thankful for little things, thankful to people","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 18, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Jabir reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever is not grateful for small things will not be grateful for large things. Whoever does not thank people has not thanked Allah Almighty.\u201d Source: al-Firdaws lil-Daylami\u0304 5962 Grade: Lahu shawahid (corroborated) according to Al-Sakhawi \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u062c\u064e\u0627\u0628\u0650\u0631\u064d \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u064e\u0651\u0628\u0650\u064a\u0650\u0651\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":820,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2011\/05\/29\/thanking-people-allah\/","url_meta":{"origin":19144,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Gratitude: Thanking people is gratefulness to Allah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 29, 2011","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever does not thank people has not thanked Allah.\u201d Source: Sunan Abi\u0304 Da\u0304wu\u0304d 4811 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0647\u064f\u0631\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u064e\u0651\u0628\u0650\u064a\u0650\u0651 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u